#: ../../source/translatingFiles.rst:127
msgid "XLIFF是处理提取出来的待翻译文本的一种XML格式。CAT软件利用这一格式存储从docx、html、idml等格式文件提取出来的文本，翻译完成后再利用这一格式文件生成目标文件。"
msgstr "XLIFF is an XML format for processing extracted text to be translated. CAT tools often use this format to store extracted text from files like docx, html and idml. When translation is done, CAT tools will generate target files based on XLIFF files."


#: ../../source/translatingFiles.rst:129
msgid "XLIFF是OASIS组织制定的标准，可以作为一种中间格式，在不同的翻译软件之间使用。"
msgstr "XLIFF is a standard formulated by the OASIS organization and can be used as an intermediate format between different translation software."


