msgid "PDF文件"
msgstr "PDF Files"


#: ../../source/translatingFiles.rst:202
msgid ""
"PDF文件是较难处理的格式，可以用Word、ABBYY、Solid Document "
"Converter等工具将其转换为Word，但原来的格式往往不能得到很好的保留。用Adobe Acrobat可以修改文字，但有诸多限制。"
msgstr "PDF file is a difficult format to process. It can be converted to docx by tools such as Word, ABBYY, Solid Document Converter, etc. But the original format can not be well preserved. Adobe Acrobat can be used to modify text, but there are many limitations."


#: ../../source/translatingFiles.rst:204
msgid "PDF文件往往是由另一种格式的文件生成的，比如docx、idml等，如果能找到源文件是最好的。如果要求保留格式却又没有源文件，只能翻译后试着重新排版。"
msgstr "PDF files are often generated by files in another format, such as docx, idml, etc. It's better to handle the source file directly. If you want to preserve the formats but do not have the source file, you have first translate text and do desktop publishing from anew."


#: ../../source/translatingFiles.rst:206
msgid "在出版社翻译InDesign文件，一般交给译员一个PDF文档，译员将译文排版成一个Word，然后交给排版人员在InDesign中进行替换。这时，我们需要做的就是提取PDF的文字进行翻译。"
msgstr "When translating InDesign documents, publishing houses often give the PDF document to the translator. The translator types the translation into a Word and then gives it to the typesetter to replace sources texts with target texts in InDesign. In such a case, what translators have to do is to extract the text from PDF."


#: ../../source/translatingFiles.rst:208
msgid "BasicCAT自带了PDF转文字的工具，可以通过菜单栏Tools->PDF2TXT打开。如果PDF的文字可以提取，那可以直接提取出来。如果不行，便使用开源的OCR软件tesseract进行识别。"
msgstr "BasicCAT has a PDF to Text tool. It can be accessed by menu "Tools->PDF2TXT". If PDF's text can be extracted, it can be extracted directly by pressing the "strip" button. If not, the open source OCR software Tesseract will be used."


#: ../../source/translatingFiles.rst:210
msgid "工具支持添加页码信息，还可以针对InDesign生成的对页进行处理。"
msgstr "You can add page number to the extracted text. It can also add facing pages number like Page 4-5."


#: ../../source/translatingFiles.rst:214
msgid "PDF中的文字是没有段落信息的，所以默认提取出来的每行文字后面都有回车，PDF2TXT提供一个reflow功能，可以自动去除多余的回车。"
msgstr "Texts in PDF do not have paragraph info. They are just fixed dots in a page. The extracted text may have newline at the end of each line. PDF2TXT provides "reflow" function to remove extra newlines."


